.TH "fimc_capture_config_update" 9 "fimc_capture_config_update" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
fimc_capture_config_update \- apply the camera interface configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" fimc_capture_config_update
.BI "(struct fimc_ctx *ctx "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
FIMC capture context
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
To be called from within the interrupt handler with fimc.slock
spinlock held. It updates the camera pixel crop, rotation and
image flip in H/W.
